      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BERNARDO BLUE (1) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (16.74) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 2.75 lengths. Rates a leading player. BIG REVEAL (4) was in trouble close to the inside last time over 390m at Q Lakeside and failed to finish. Has the ability and can measure up. HOLD THE GAVEL (2) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Found it a bit far latest when finished sixth over 407m at Rockhampton (24.28) in a Free For All but is better suited back in trip here. Has a strong record at this distance including six wins. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. APOLLO'S SUN (6) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
